<article about="/project/swiss-leaks" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document" class="node node-project node-promoted node-sticky node-published author-hbolandrudder odd clearfix" id="node-project-1049">
        <span property="dc:title" content="Swiss Leaks: Murky Cash Sheltered by Bank Secrecy" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>    
  

  <div class="content clearfix">

    
            <div id="marquee" class="marquee-image">
        <a href="/project/swiss-leaks/banking-giant-hsbc-sheltered-murky-cash-linked-dictators-and-arms-dealers"><div class="field field-name-field-marqueeimage field-type-image field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://cloudfront-9.icij.org/sites/icij/files/styles/project_marqueewide/public/projects/swissleaks_icij_large_no_text.jpg?itok=W07JudPW" width="920" height="510" alt="" /></div></div></div></a>

        <div class="marquee-blurb">
          <h3><a href="/project/swiss-leaks/banking-giant-hsbc-sheltered-murky-cash-linked-dictators-and-arms-dealers"><div class="field field-name-field-marqueetitle field-type-text field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Private Bank Secrets Revealed</div></div></div></a></h3>
          <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"> A team of journalists from 45 countries has unearthed secret bank accounts maintained for criminals, traffickers, tax dodgers, politicians and celebrities. </div></div></div>		    <div class="read-more"><a href="http://www.icij.org/project/swiss-leaks/banking-giant-hsbc-sheltered-murky-cash-linked-dictators-and-arms-dealers">View &#x25B8;</a></div>
        </div>
          </div>
    <div class="view view-project-articles view-id-project_articles view-display-id-highlighted_block project-articles project-highlighted view-dom-id-634811b6657f045c9ee06fd5e032beb8">
        
  
  
      <div class="view-content">
        <div class="highlight">
      
          <a href="http://www.icij.org/project/swiss-leaks/explore-swiss-leaks-data"><a href="/project/swiss-leaks/explore-swiss-leaks-data"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://cloudfront-6.icij.org/sites/icij/files/styles/highlighted/public/1200-interactivegraphic.jpg?itok=TUBatbf6" width="299" height="180" alt="" /></a></a>    
  <h3>        <a href="http://www.icij.org/project/swiss-leaks/explore-swiss-leaks-data">Explore the Swiss Leaks Data</a>  </h3>  
           Based on a trove of 60,000 leaked files, with details on over 100,000 HSBC clients, explore the data country by country, and see a sample of the bank's clients.     </div>
  <div class="highlight">
      
          <a href="http://www.icij.org/project/swiss-leaks/whistleblower-thief-hero-introducing-source-data-shook-hsbc"><a href="/project/swiss-leaks/whistleblower-thief-hero-introducing-source-data-shook-hsbc"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://cloudfront-8.icij.org/sites/icij/files/styles/highlighted/public/screen-shot-2015-02-03-at-7.03.00-pm.jpg?itok=2Aerfh0q" width="299" height="180" alt="Hervé Falciani." title="Hervé Falciani styles himself as part James Bond, part disappointed idealist. But who is he really? Photo: Le Monde" /></a></a>    
  <h3>        <a href="http://www.icij.org/project/swiss-leaks/whistleblower-thief-hero-introducing-source-data-shook-hsbc">Whistleblower? Thief? Hero?</a>  </h3>  
           Hervé Falciani has taken a long, strange journey from bank computer expert to jailed fugitive to candidate for office to whistleblower spokesman.     </div>
  <div class="highlight">
      
          <a href="http://www.icij.org/project/swiss-leaks/real-housewives-hsbc"><a href="/project/swiss-leaks/real-housewives-hsbc"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://cloudfront-10.icij.org/sites/icij/files/styles/highlighted/public/1200-generic-jet-shutterstock_176621102.jpg?itok=qgxhwnH3" width="299" height="180" alt="Woman boarding a private jet" title="Women listed as &quot;housewives&quot; by HSBC aren&#039;t always what they&#039;d seem. Photo: Shutterstock" /></a></a>    
  <h3>        <a href="http://www.icij.org/project/swiss-leaks/real-housewives-hsbc">The Real &#039;Housewives&#039; of HSBC</a>  </h3>  
           When accounts in the leaked files list a profession, "housewife" pops up with amazing frequency. But these so-called housewives are not always what they seem.     </div>
    </div>
  
  
  
  
  
  
</div>
