<article about="/project/swiss-leaks/new-countries-seek-hsbc-data-and-undeclared-cash" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document" class="node node-article node-sticky node-teaser node-published node-not-promoted author-hbolandrudder even clearfix" id="node-article-1082">

  
    <header>
    <div class="field field-name-field-project-label-listing-head field-type-text field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Tax investigations</div></div></div>    <h2 class="node-title"><a href="http://www.icij.org/project/swiss-leaks/new-countries-seek-hsbc-data-and-undeclared-cash" title="New Countries Seek HSBC Data and Undeclared Cash">New Countries Seek HSBC Data and Undeclared Cash</a></h2>
  </header>
    

  <div class="content clearfix">

      <div class="field field-name-field-marqueeimage field-type-image field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/project/swiss-leaks/new-countries-seek-hsbc-data-and-undeclared-cash"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://cloudfront-7.icij.org/sites/icij/files/styles/article_thumbnail/public/1200-hmrc-tax-campaign.jpg?itok=U2FUjU3u" width="150" height="83" alt="HMRC tax campaign" title="A campaign run by British tax authorities in 2012 warned against undeclared income. Photo: HMRC" /></a></div></div></div>  
  <div id="main-content-wrapper">

	  
  <footer class="submitted"><address class="byline" rel="sioc:has_creator">By <a href="/contributors/martha-m-hamilton" typeof="sioc:UserAccount" property="foaf:name" about="contributors/martha-m-hamilton">Martha M. Hamilton</a>, <a href="/contributors/jakob-sorgenfri" typeof="sioc:UserAccount" property="foaf:name" about="contributors/jakob-sorgenfri">Jakob Sorgenfri</a> and <a href="/journalists/john-hansen" typeof="sioc:UserAccount" property="foaf:name" about="journalists/john-hansen">John Hansen</a></address> <time><div class="field field-name-field-pubdate field-type-date field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><span class="date-display-single" property="dc:date" datatype="xsd:dateTime" content="2015-02-23T06:30:00-05:00">February 23, 2015, 6:30 am</span></div></div></div></time></footer>

    
  <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"> With the release of a treasure trove of data about how HSBC helped clients shield income from tax collectors, more nations are asking France for the data, while other countries face growing demands from critics to do more in the hunt for lost tax revenue. </div></div></div>      <span class="read-more"><a href="http://www.icij.org/project/swiss-leaks/new-countries-seek-hsbc-data-and-undeclared-cash">Read more <span class="element-invisible">about New Countries Seek HSBC Data and Undeclared Cash</span></a></span>
  
