<article about="/project/swiss-leaks/60-minutes-stolen-data-shakes-swiss-banking-its-core" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document" class="node node-multimedia-clip node-teaser node-published node-not-promoted node-not-sticky author-hbolandrudder odd clearfix" id="node-multimedia-clip-1070">

