  </header>
    
  <div class="content clearfix">
  
      <div class="field field-name-field-marqueeimage field-type-image field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/project/swiss-leaks/60-minutes-stolen-data-shakes-swiss-banking-its-core"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://cloudfront-6.icij.org/sites/icij/files/styles/article_thumbnail/public/920-60mins.jpg?itok=75-PpLNb" width="150" height="83" alt="" /></a></div></div></div>	
  <div id="main-content-wrapper">  
    <footer class="submitted"><address class="byline" rel="sioc:has_creator">By <a href="/contributors/habiba-nosheen" typeof="sioc:UserAccount" property="foaf:name" about="contributors/habiba-nosheen">Habiba Nosheen</a>, <a href="/contributors/ira-rosen" typeof="sioc:UserAccount" property="foaf:name" about="contributors/ira-rosen">Ira Rosen</a> and <a href="/contributors/bill-whitaker" typeof="sioc:UserAccount" property="foaf:name" about="contributors/bill-whitaker">Bill Whitaker</a></address> <time><div class="field field-name-field-pubdate field-type-date field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><span class="date-display-single" property="dc:date" datatype="xsd:dateTime" content="2015-02-08T23:00:00-05:00">Sunday, February 8, 2015 - 11:00pm</span></div></div></div></time></footer>

    
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"> The largest and most damaging Swiss bank heist in history doesn't involve stolen money but stolen computer files with more than 100,000 names tied to Swiss bank accounts at HSBC, the second largest commercial bank in the world. </div></div></div>          <span class="read-more"><a href="http://www.icij.org/project/swiss-leaks/60-minutes-stolen-data-shakes-swiss-banking-its-core">Read more <span class="element-invisible">about 60 Minutes: Stolen Data Shakes Swiss Banking to its Core</span></a></span>
        
    
