</div></section><section class="project-about"><div class="view view-project-contextual-sidebar view-id-project_contextual_sidebar view-display-id-contextual_sidebar_about project-content project-sidebar project-about view-dom-id-25e1d3c5c92f13cb47474b5238c32b3a">
        
  
  
      <div class="view-content">
        <div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first views-row-last">
      
  <div>        <div><h2 class="block-title"><a href="http://www.icij.org/project/swiss-leaks/about-project-swiss-leaks">About This Project</a></h2>
<div> <p><span style="line-height: 1.3;"><a href="/swissleaks">Swiss Leaks</a> is a collaborative investigation that exposes how the Swiss branch of one of the world’s biggest banks, HSBC, <a href="https://www.icij.org/project/swiss-leaks/banking-giant-hsbc-sheltered-murky-cash-linked-dictators-and-arms-dealers">profited</a> from doing business with tax dodgers and criminals around the world. </span></p></div><br><a href="http://www.icij.org/project/swiss-leaks/about-project-swiss-leaks">Read more</a></div>  </div>  </div>
    </div>
  
  
  
  
  
  
